I’m happy to announce that I have just founded and started my first company, DBR Studios, LLC 🎻

DuBose Rene’ Studios is an Entertainment Production Company that plays at all events  and changes the world through music 🎶 (𝘢𝘤𝘤𝘦𝘴𝘴 𝘵𝘰 𝘢𝘭𝘭 𝘱𝘢𝘨𝘦𝘴 𝘢𝘯𝘥 𝘸𝘦𝘣𝘴𝘪𝘵𝘦𝘴 𝘰𝘯 𝘐𝘯𝘴𝘵𝘢𝘨𝘳𝘢𝘮 𝘵𝘢𝘨𝘴 𝘢𝘣𝘰𝘷𝘦 𝘢𝘯𝘥 𝘭𝘪𝘯𝘬 𝘪𝘯 𝘣𝘪𝘰)

To add on, I have started a Partnership with my good friend @alex.carriles and his Creative Design Studio @acstudiosx 🎥 

We are in the process of creating a unique and custom 3D Printed ElectroAcoustic Violin. All branding, logos and designs are made by Alex Carriles. 

More soon to come…
